289
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,120
And then we'll help you.

290
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:49,300
We did it!

291
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:54,940
We'll kill Oniguma, and we'll bring
home its hide and eyes as proof.

292
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:58,870
