295
00:19:05,140 --> 00:19:06,920
No, we have to.

296
00:19:07,410 --> 00:19:08,750
No matter what.

297
00:19:10,840 --> 00:19:13,730
Right, Onee-chan?

298
00:19:33,410 --> 00:19:36,690
You're just like me, huh?

299
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:43,900
People said I was special and
amazing when I left Ninannah.

300
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:46,330
