once your wounds heal.

311
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,670
You can go home.

312
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:11,490
I'm sorry I made you feel uneasy.

313
00:20:11,670 --> 00:20:12,930
I'm sorry.

