00:20:23,280 --> 00:20:24,260
It hurts.

319
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:32,780
Thank you.

320
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:55,880
The vessel opened.

321
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:09,590
Oniguma is dead.

322
00:21:09,930 --> 00:21:11,960
They'll come retrieve the body by tomorrow.

323
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:14,890
We need to escape with the proof first.

324
00:21:15,340 --> 00:21:18,030
We'll be out of here in no time, March.

325
00:21:18,290 --> 00:21:21,030
You don't need to become a
grown-up in this damn place.

326
00:21:39,620 --> 00:21:40,430
Over there!

327
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:43,910
Onee-chan!

328
00:21:44,650 --> 00:21:46,140
It hurts.

329
00:21:52,150 --> 00:21:55,810
Looks like I'm in a storage room.

330
00:21:58,940 --> 00:22:01,200
Look who it is.

331
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,290
It's you.

332
00:22:02,710 --> 00:22:06,470
I won't tell anyone that
you tried to run away.

333
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,490
So just do as I say.

334
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:17,630
How dare you?!

335
00:22:20,430 --> 00:22:21,750
I won't tell anyone.

336
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:23,890
So do as I say.

337
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,230
Shift's up.

338
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:34,500
You!

339
00:22:35,620 --> 00:22:37,660
